  "body": "### Info\nRemoves the steve figure from the new minecraft capes, Home and Menace. I personally do not like it so thats why I made this. This is an extremely inefficent way to do this but who cares, it works. It works in completely vanilla minecraft, no mods required!\n\n### Showcase\n![Example of the Home cape changes](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/SxpRZYW5/images/1b04cdcfd8aceffe2cde8bc7e94cc7024cc989bc.png)\n\n![Example of the Menace cape changes](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/SxpRZYW5/images/ab9f4de158e3c49541c5fb52761f27e133ce5dcd.png)\n\n![Example of the Yearn cape changes](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/SxpRZYW5/images/f733d0be82484fdd630b24bc01bf570765077500.png)\n\n# Other\n### Want to use this with my other packs?\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/blues-core-shaders\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/IFZoFQQs/f2f1a4985a734d66f86b87bb8a122a28b3282fd4_96.webp\" alt=\"Blue's Core Shaders\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\">\n</a>\n\nThe above pack combines all of the following:\n\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/emissive-office-cape\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/HdOx2YHC/cf95c8b4178ded5eeaac680be4098458455c1cc4_96.webp\" alt=\"Emissive Office Cape\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/emissive-trims\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/gxUihgVw/fc96bb5326578f80b1a245ecce2555373d47cdef.png\" alt=\"Emissive Trims\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/emissive-cape-portals\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/K0psvV8X/34840719349cbcdafe8e4e78ec02c8253256ada4.png\" alt=\"Emissive Cape portals\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/emissive-twitch-cape\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/dpiEWPp1/c3315e8bbbc049400a2166d5fb218cac8047365d_96.webp\" alt=\"Emissive Twitch Cape\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/i-am-not-steve\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/SxpRZYW5/d282e7848bca5aab9bc969480d200f3c09c137b6_96.webp\" alt=\"I am not steve\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\">\n</a>",
